### Missing name — expect 400
POST {{host}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "No name provided",
  "price": 10.00,
  "quantityAvailable": 5
}

### Negative price — expect 400
POST {{host}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid product",
  "description": "Price below minimum",
  "price": -1.00,
  "quantityAvailable": 5
}

### Negative quantity — expect 400
POST {{host}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid product",
  "description": "Quantity below zero",
  "price": 10.00,
  "quantityAvailable": -3
}

### Name too long (>100 chars) — expect 400
POST {{host}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA",
  "description": "Too long",
  "price": 10.00,
  "quantityAvailable": 5
}

### Non-existent product — expect 404
GET {{host}}/api/v1/products/999999
Accept: application/json
